metadata.title: T&S profiles - NW Pacific, Bering, Okhotsk (Russia)
metadata.description:
Standard transects at various locations in the NW Pacific. Bering Sea and Sea of Okhotsk.

Geographical Area:
NW Pacific, Sea of Okhotsk and Bering Sea

Distributions of observations by year/by month available from PICES office, as well as details on the location of the sections. Some of these data may be included in the World Ocean Atlas 1994

A TCODE project
